&nbsp;
To the damage caused by cementification, are added those of the wild photovoltaic - denounces Coldiretti - with the cover of entire productive agricultural areas with stretches of hectares of panels on the ground. Plants often made from speculative investment funds and made possible by a normative far west that derives from the absence of rules of government of the territory.
